ic</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇我個名梗係正評位留比王子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你個topic就咪鬼韋拿放係前面啦 fake人"},{"pid":"c962dfd54216abcac134bfdf83c0d9019b19f99d","tid":90352,"uid":7199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"費托全盛 &gt; 韋拿全盛 <br />\n韋拿生涯 &gt; 費托生涯<br />\n講鍾意我簡費托 全盛太突出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d068e7ef26b05dc8a7008673607094f1cfbf36","tid":90352,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:44:22.000Z","msg":"villa帶領馬體會 薩拉戈薩 華倫西亞拎盃 <br />\n廢托呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699df0857efc5a60313c691d205cebc4ec918c64","tid":90352,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T06:47:26.000Z","msg":"費托全盛時期冇人阻到佢<br />\n又快又扭得，腳頭又勁<br />\n同bug一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ac08d6861ab75227515b290d077a5e429a56a7","tid":90352,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>費托全盛時期冇人阻到佢<br />\n又快又扭得，腳頭又勁<br />\n同bug一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger. <br />\n<br />\n可惜全盛太短"},{"pid":"b4989f171acbe236d788cd91e2c2f8ec4613e9e1","tid":90352,"uid":37827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T10:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>費托全盛時期冇人阻到佢<br />\n又快又扭得，腳頭又勁<br />\n同bug一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n球會隊友阻